title: Guardians of the Galaxy

title: Split

title: Sing

title: Suicide Squad

title: The Great Wall

title: La La Land

title: Mindhorn

title: The Lost City of Z
creator: James Gray
description: A true-life drama, centering on British explorer Col. Percival Fawcett, who disappeared while searching for a mysterious city in the Amazon in the 1920s.

title: Passengers
creator: Morten Tyldum
description: A spacecraft traveling to a distant colony planet and transporting thousands of people has a malfunction in its sleep chambers. As a result, two passengers are awakened 90 years early.

title: Fantastic Beasts and Where to Find Them
creator: David Yates
description: The adventures of writer Newt Scamander in New York's secret community of witches and wizards seventy years before Harry Potter reads his book in school.

title: Hidden Figures
creator: Theodore Melfi
description: The story of a team of female African-American mathematicians who served a vital role in NASA during the early years of the U.S. space program.

title: Rogue One
creator: Gareth Edwards
description: The Rebel Alliance makes a risky move to steal the plans for the Death Star, setting up the epic saga to follow.

title: Moana
creator: Ron Clements
description: In Ancient Polynesia, when a terrible curse incurred by the Demigod Maui reaches an impetuous Chieftain's daughter's island, she answers the Ocean's call to seek out the Demigod to set things right.

title: Colossal
creator: Nacho Vigalondo
description: Gloria is an out-of-work party girl forced to leave her life in New York City, and move back home. When reports surface that a giant creature is destroying Seoul, she gradually comes to the realization that she is somehow connected to this phenomenon.

title: The Secret Life of Pets
creator: Chris Renaud
description: The quiet life of a terrier named Max is upended when his owner takes in Duke, a stray whom Max instantly dislikes.

title: Hacksaw Ridge
creator: Mel Gibson
description: WWII American Army Medic Desmond T. Doss, who served during the Battle of Okinawa, refuses to kill people, and becomes the first man in American history to receive the Medal of Honor without firing a shot.

title: Jason Bourne
creator: Paul Greengrass
description: The CIA's most dangerous former operative is drawn out of hiding to uncover more explosive truths about his past.

title: Lion
creator: Garth Davis
description: A five-year-old Indian boy gets lost on the streets of Calcutta, thousands of kilometers from home. He survives many challenges before being adopted by a couple in Australia. 25 years later, he sets out to find his lost family.

title: Arrival
creator: Denis Villeneuve
description: When twelve mysterious spacecraft appear around the world, linguistics professor Louise Banks is tasked with interpreting the language of the apparent alien visitors.

title: Gold
creator: Stephen Gaghan
description: Kenny Wells, a prospector desperate for a lucky break, teams up with a similarly eager geologist and sets off on a journey to find gold in the uncharted jungle of Indonesia.

title: Manchester by the Sea
creator: Kenneth Lonergan
description: A depressed uncle is asked to take care of his teenage nephew after the boy's father dies.

title: Hounds of Love
creator: Ben Young
description: A cold-blooded predatory couple while cruising the streets in search of their next victim, will stumble upon a 17-year-old high school girl, who will be sedated, abducted and chained in the strangers' guest room.

title: Trolls
creator: Walt Dohrn
description: After the Bergens invade Troll Village, Poppy, the happiest Troll ever born, and the curmudgeonly Branch set off on a journey to rescue her friends.

title: Independence Day: Resurgence
creator: Roland Emmerich
description: Two decades after the first Independence Day invasion, Earth is faced with a new extra-Solar threat. But will mankind's new space defenses be enough?

title: Paris pieds nus
creator: Dominique Abel
description: Fiona visits Paris for the first time to assist her myopic Aunt Martha. Catastrophes ensue, mainly involving Dom, a homeless man who has yet to have an emotion or thought he was afraid of expressing.

title: Bahubali: The Beginning
creator: S.S. Rajamouli
description: In ancient India, an adventurous and daring man becomes involved in a decades old feud between two warring people.

title: Dead Awake
creator: Phillip Guzman
description: A young woman must save herself and her friends from an ancient evil that stalks its victims through the real-life phenomenon of sleep paralysis.

title: Bad Moms
creator: Jon Lucas
description: When three overworked and under-appreciated moms are pushed beyond their limits, they ditch their conventional responsibilities for a jolt of long overdue freedom, fun, and comedic self-indulgence.

title: Assassin's Creed
creator: Justin Kurzel
description: When Callum Lynch explores the memories of his ancestor Aguilar and gains the skills of a Master Assassin, he discovers he is a descendant of the secret Assassins society.

title: Why Him?
creator: John Hamburg
description: A holiday gathering threatens to go off the rails when Ned Fleming realizes that his daughter's Silicon Valley millionaire boyfriend is about to pop the question.

title: Nocturnal Animals
creator: Tom Ford
description: A wealthy art gallery owner is haunted by her ex-husband's novel, a violent thriller she interprets as a symbolic revenge tale.

title: X-Men: Apocalypse
creator: Bryan Singer
description: After the re-emergence of the world's first mutant, world-destroyer Apocalypse, the X-Men must unite to defeat his extinction level plan.

title: Deadpool
creator: Tim Miller
description: A fast-talking mercenary with a morbid sense of humor is subjected to a rogue experiment that leaves him with accelerated healing powers and a quest for revenge.

title: Resident Evil: The Final Chapter
creator: Paul W.S. Anderson
description: Alice returns to where the nightmare began: The Hive in Raccoon City, where the Umbrella Corporation is gathering its forces for a final strike against the only remaining survivors of the apocalypse.

title: Captain America: Civil War
creator: Anthony Russo
description: Political interference in the Avengers' activities causes a rift between former allies Captain America and Iron Man.

title: Interstellar
creator: Christopher Nolan
description: A team of explorers travel through a wormhole in space in an attempt to ensure humanity's survival.

title: Doctor Strange
creator: Scott Derrickson
description: While on a journey of physical and spiritual healing, a brilliant neurosurgeon is drawn into the world of the mystic arts.

title: The Magnificent Seven
creator: Antoine Fuqua
description: Seven gunmen in the old west gradually come together to help a poor village against savage thieves.

creator: Patrick Read Johnson
description: Alienated, hopeful-filmmaker Pat Johnson's epic story growing up in rural Illinois, falling in love, and becoming the first fan of the movie that changed everything.

title: Sausage Party
creator: Greg Tiernan
description: A sausage strives to discover the truth about his existence.

title: Moonlight
creator: Barry Jenkins
description: A chronicle of the childhood, adolescence and burgeoning adulthood of a young, African-American, gay man growing up in a rough neighborhood of Miami.

title: Don't Fuck in the Woods
creator: Shawn Burkett
description: A group of friends are going on a camping trip to celebrate graduating college. But once they enter the woods, the proverbial shit starts to hit the fan.

title: The Founder
creator: John Lee Hancock
description: The story of Ray Kroc, a salesman who turned two brothers' innovative fast food eatery, McDonald's, into one of the biggest restaurant businesses in the world with a combination of ambition, persistence, and ruthlessness.

title: Lowriders
creator: Ricardo de Montreuil
description: A young street artist in East Los Angeles is caught between his father's obsession with lowrider car culture, his ex-felon brother and his need for self-expression.

title: Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides
creator: Rob Marshall
description: Jack Sparrow and Barbossa embark on a quest to find the elusive fountain of youth, only to discover that Blackbeard and his daughter are after it too.

title: Miss Sloane
creator: John Madden
description: In the high-stakes world of political power-brokers, Elizabeth Sloane is the most sought after and formidable lobbyist in D.C. But when taking on the most powerful opponent of her career, she finds winning may come at too high a price.

title: Fallen
creator: Scott Hicks
description: A young girl finds herself in a reform school after therapy since she was blamed for the death of a young boy. At the school she finds herself drawn to a fellow student, unaware that he is an angel, and has loved her for thousands of years.

title: Star Trek Beyond
creator: Justin Lin
description: The USS Enterprise crew explores the furthest reaches of uncharted space, where they encounter a new ruthless enemy who puts them and everything the Federation stands for to the test.

title: The Last Face
creator: Sean Penn
description: A director (Charlize Theron) of an international aid agency in Africa meets a relief aid doctor (Javier Bardem) amidst a political/social revolution, and together face tough choices ... See full summary »

title: Star Wars: Episode VII - The Force Awakens
creator: J.J. Abrams
description: Three decades after the defeat of the Galactic Empire, a new threat arises. The First Order attempts to rule the galaxy and only a ragtag group of heroes can stop them, along with the help of the Resistance.

title: Underworld: Blood Wars
creator: Anna Foerster
description: Vampire death dealer, Selene (Kate Beckinsale) fights to end the eternal war between the Lycan clan and the Vampire faction that betrayed her.

title: Mother's Day
creator: Garry Marshall
description: Three generations come together in the week leading up to Mother's Day.

title: John Wick
creator: Chad Stahelski
description: An ex-hitman comes out of retirement to track down the gangsters that took everything from him.

title: The Dark Knight
creator: Christopher Nolan
description: When the menace known as the Joker wreaks havoc and chaos on the people of Gotham, the Dark Knight must come to terms with one of the greatest psychological tests of his ability to fight injustice.

title: Silence
creator: Martin Scorsese
description: In the 17th century, two Portuguese Jesuit priests travel to Japan in an attempt to locate their mentor, who is rumored to have committed apostasy, and to propagate Catholicism.

title: Don't Breathe
creator: Fede Alvarez
description: Hoping to walk away with a massive fortune, a trio of thieves break into the house of a blind man who isn't as helpless as he seems.

title: Me Before You
creator: Thea Sharrock
description: A girl in a small town forms an unlikely bond with a recently-paralyzed man she's taking care of.

title: Their Finest
creator: Lone Scherfig
description: A former secretary, newly appointed as a scriptwriter for propaganda films, joins the cast and crew of a major production while the Blitz rages around them.

title: Sully
creator: Clint Eastwood
description: The story of Chesley Sullenberger, an American pilot who became a hero after landing his damaged plane on the Hudson River in order to save the flight's passengers and crew.

title: Batman v Superman: Dawn of Justice
creator: Zack Snyder
description: Fearing that the actions of Superman are left unchecked, Batman takes on the Man of Steel, while the world wrestles with what kind of a hero it really needs.
